{"name":"Soulfire","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>The purifying flames of Sigmar surround you, as his wrath manifests on earth. Centre the large template on yourself. Those affected take a Damage 3 hit. Undead and Daemons have it even worse, suffering a Damage 5 hit. Armour offers no protection against soulfire.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Divine Lore (Sigmar)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":"3"},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":20},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Half Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A golden amulet engraved with the comet of Simgar","bonus":2},"template":{"value":"large"}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"Ki5Q1Reg3uUs6Tmb"}
{"name":"Healing Hand","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>Your touch heals an injured character of 1d10 Wounds. You can also heal yourself. This is a touch spell.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Divine Lore (Sigmar)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":12},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"1 Full Action and 1 Half Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A leather glove","bonus":2},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"ZB1EuLY47uxn5ej8"}
{"name":"Armour of Righteousness","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>A nimbus of power protects you from harm. You gain +1 Armour Point on all locations, though the maximum of 5 APs still applies. Armour of righteousness lasts for one minute per point of your Magic Characteristic.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Divine Lore (Sigmar)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":6},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Full Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A small iron ring","bonus":1},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"afTUkKirGGzYk9sL"}
{"name":"Beacon Of Courage","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>The power and majesty of Sigmar fills you, making you shine out like a beacon in the night. Any frightened or terrified ally who can see you is inspired by your faith and bravery. Such characters immediately recover and can now act normally.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Divine Lore (Sigmar)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":14},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Half Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A prism","bonus":2},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"eCe4PZrBtfAPFPkC"}
{"name":"Hammer Of Sigmar","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>Your hammer is imbued with Sigmar’s power. Your hand weapon, which must be a hammer, counts as having the Impact quality and as magical for 1 minute (6 rounds).</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Divine Lore (Sigmar)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":5},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Half Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A charm engraved with the symbol of Sigmar","bonus":1},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"uEOwATcvjNWzd8EC"}
